{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 DR_ODINE_Translator\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Converts Program Change messages to Key Switch notes or CCs based on loaded maps. Features mapped and unmapped modes with automatic switching via AutoSwitcher.lua. Uses shared memory (gmem) to store mapping configurations with UI display.\par}
}

