{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 DR_ODINE_Unmapped Note Shortener\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Shortens note lengths based on CC119 articulation markers. Handles note aliasing issues with proper note-off management. Prevents stuck notes when disabled and tracks scheduled offs across blocks.\par}
}

